  "opening_lines": [
    {
      "line": 1,
      "text": "_ JANUARY a"
    },
    {
      "line": 2,
      "text": "_ ~‘Whole Earth Catalog 1"
    },
    {
      "line": 5,
      "text": "The $1 Catalog was formerly called the SUPPLEMENT to the Whole Earth Catalog. The name was changed to accomodate the Post Office."
    },
    {
      "line": 6,
      "text": "Grim details on p. 53. ‘"
    },
    {
      "line": 9,
      "text": "CBS Radio"
    },
    {
      "line": 12,
      "text": "THE AREA"
    },
    {
      "line": 15,
      "text": "From Arthur Godfrey to Esquire"
    },
    {
      "line": 18,
      "text": "IN RESPONSE TO YOUR KIND INVITATION OF INCREDIBLE AS IT MAY SEEM, MAN NOW FINDS HIMSELF"
    },
    {
      "line": 21,
      "text": "JULY 9TH, IT STRIKES ME THAT THE CHALLENGES ACTUALLY LISTED AS ONE OF THE ENDANGERED SPECIES,"
    },
    {
      "line": 22,
      "text": "FACING ALL OF MANKIND ON THIS PLANET IN NOT IN THE NEXT THOUSAND YEARS OR EVEN THE NEXT"
    },
    {
      "line": 23,
      "text": "THE SEVENTIES HAVE NOW RESOLVED THEMSELVES HUNDRED-BUT WITHIN THE NEXT THIRTY YEARS-"
    },
    {
      "line": 25,
      "text": "INTO A VERY SIMPLE ONE: SURVIVAL. ALL THAT'S LEFT OF THE TWENTIETH CENTURY."
    },
    {
      "line": 31,
      "text": "FUNCTION : a"
    },
    {
      "line": 34,
      "text": "The WHOLE EARTH CATALOG functions as an evaluation and access"
    },
    {
      "line": 35,
      "text": "device. With it, the user should know better what is worth getting and"
    },
    {
      "line": 36,
      "text": "where and how to do the getting."
    },
    {
      "line": 39,
      "text": "An item is listed in the CATALOG if it is deemed:"
    },
    {
      "line": 40,
      "text": "1) Useful as a tool,"
    },
    {
      "line": 41,
      "text": "2) Relevant to independent education,"
    },
    {
      "line": 42,
      "text": "3) High quality or low cost,"
    },
    {
      "line": 43,
      "text": "4) Easily available by mail."
    },
    {
      "line": 46,
      "text": "CATALOG listings are continually revised according to the experience"
    },
    {
      "line": 47,
      "text": "and suggestions of CATALOG .users and staff."
    },
    {
      "line": 50,
      "text": "PURPOSE"
    },
    {
      "line": 53,
      "text": "We are as gods and might as well get good at it. So far remotely done"
    },
    {
      "line": 54,
      "text": "power and glory-as via government, big business, formal education,"
    },
    {
      "line": 55,
      "text": "church-has succeeded to the point where gross defects obscure actual"
    },
    {
      "line": 56,
      "text": "gains. In response to this dilemma and to these gains a realm of intimate,"
    },
    {
      "line": 57,
      "text": "personal power is developing-power of the individual to conduct his own"
    },
    {
      "line": 58,
      "text": "education, find his own inspiration, shape his own environment, and"
    },
    {
      "line": 59,
      "text": "share his adventure with whoever is interested."
    },
    {
      "line": 60,
      "text": "process are sought and promoted by the WHOLE EARTH CATALOG."
